{"tid":718863,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"中國官媒吹噓新四大發明　科技日報總編：誤國害民","createTime":"2018-06-27T04:24:59.000Z","updateTime":"2018-06-27T07:06:53.000Z","uid":75969,"like":27,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"4fd428434c7eaceaf6d4be4fa07c6d66ac55568e","tid":718863,"uid":75969,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-27T04:24:59.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.appledaily.com.tw/images/ReNews/20180627/640_81bddbd70e72daf411d9dd2f1ffbc54d.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.appledaily.com.tw%2Fimages%2FReNews%2F20180627%2F640_81bddbd70e72daf411d9dd2f1ffbc54d.jpg&h=6257cde8&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: small;\">劉亞東。　翻攝中國《科技日報》<br />\n</span><br />\n<br />\n中國官媒自去年5月起，不斷發文聲稱，中國發明了高鐵、行動支付（如：支付寶）、電子商務（網路購物）和共享單車，對外宣傳這是中國的「新四大發明」。對此，中國《科技日報》總編輯劉亞東，近日在北京的一個論壇上，直言這根本是「自欺欺人」。他更猛批，這些都是官媒「忽悠（欺騙）領導，忽悠公眾，甚至忽悠了自己」、「誇大科技成就，誤國害民」。<br />\n <br />\n劉亞東早前出席名為《是甚麼卡了我們的脖子?亟待攻克的核心技術》的論壇，主辦單位原本要他討論美、中貿易磨擦，及美國對中國的技術制裁。沒想到，劉亞東沒有如其他來賓般批評美國，反而大罵中國的智庫及官媒。<br />\n <br />\n劉亞東直言，中國科技與美國及西方相比，有很大的差距，這本來是常識，「可是國內偏偏有些人，一會兒說新四大發明，一會兒說全面趕超、主體超越，吹噓中國現時經濟、科技實力、綜合國力都分別超越美國，世界第一；還算得有整有零，有鼻子有眼兒」、「這種誇大其詞的與論，無論出於甚麼動機，都有百害而無一利，結果是誤國害民」。<br />\n <br />\n英國廣播公司（BBC）早前曾一一查核指出，高鐵、行動支付、電子商務和共享單車，早在數十年前就被發明出來，中國沒有發明任何這些技術，只是在推廣應用上處於領先。（大陸中心／綜合外電報導）<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://tw.news.appledaily.com/international/realtime/20180627/1380469/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftw.news.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2Frealtime%2F20180627%2F1380469%2F&d=zM35jLS05zISECKmFrxpgBOFz4pMHIf1Ti9x7C0XgVU%3D&h=93d38be8\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftw.news.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2Frealtime%2F20180627%2F1380469%2F&h=8f5abb82\" target=\"_blank\">https://tw.news.appledaily.com/international/realtime/20180627/1380469/</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://vignette.wikia.nocookie.net/evchk/images/9/99/Byesacr3.gif/revision/latest?cb=20071111140822\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fvignette.wikia.nocookie.net%2Fevchk%2Fimages%2F9%2F99%2FByesacr3.gif%2Frevision%2Flatest%3Fcb%3D20071111140822&h=a0c1dc7a&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"e1d77cc1e802bcd5d9767d95c731adec28a98fa2","tid":718863,"uid":143499,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-27T06:24:31.000Z","msg":"好彩佢有一百蚊，唔係打靶都似<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7525e166d28ae346cda728affb04e2ad69b6b879","tid":718863,"uid":192052,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-27T06:27:40.000Z","msg":"JR<br />\nAmazon ebay <br />\nQR方面好似冇<br />\n<br />\n共享算四大發明咩？"},{"pid":"0393cddb90627e85d4b2333c3e79102f6d68479b","tid":718863,"uid":30169,"like":0,"dislike":4,"score":-4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-27T06:35:58.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/06/27/143556_0ff296ae8e61f7031c23d18fa2cd688c.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F06%2F27%2F143556_0ff296ae8e61f7031c23d18fa2cd688c.png&h=7345eb9a&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"1870e8fcee8694a82f4da2832f3455d04a312424","tid":718863,"uid":93784,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-27T06:37:46.000Z","msg":"知唔知咩叫發明? <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"539a8f91e9f477d92be3849a89af717a47a08345","tid":718863,"uid":44454,"like":14,"dislike":0,"score":14,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-27T06:41:15.000Z","msg":"中國發明了埋葬高鐵、監控支付丶假貨網購丶共偷單車<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n新四大發明"},{"pid":"e29c13fa5caf5525fd0f5048a9cba858918bdc48","tid":718863,"uid":22566,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-27T06:43:19.000Z","msg":"最強大嘅自煮燃法竟然冇份<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"77c16f2ac01ad223b9e7a97c7ef322c3c4a66d5d","tid":718863,"uid":18120,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"7525e1